    "In musculoskeletal oncology, most AI-based radiomic studies focused on prediction of diagnosis-such as benign versus malignant tumor discrimination [72] or tumor grading [73]-and outcome-such as therapy response [27,74], recurrence [28,75], and survival [29].",
